<section class="tw-rh2">
  <div class="tw-rh2-grid">
    <div>
      <h1 class="tw-rh2-title">Your guide in <em>buying and selling.</em></h1>
      <p class="tw-rh2-lede">One of Maryland&rsquo;s few family-owned brokerages that has <strong>managed your rental, maintained your rental, and can now sell your rental</strong> &mdash; with knowledge of its full management history. Built for investment-minded buyers and sellers.</p>
      <div class="tw-rh2-actions">
        <a href="/request-a-proposal" class="tw-btn tw-btn-primary tw-btn-lg">Request a market analysis</a>
        <a href="#lifecycle" class="tw-btn tw-btn-ghost">See the lifecycle advantage <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="13 6 19 12 13 18"/></svg></a>
      </div>
      <div class="tw-rh2-meta">
        <div class="tw-rh2-meta-cell"><span class="num">35+</span><span class="lab">Years in MD market</span></div>
        <div class="tw-rh2-meta-cell"><span class="num">MD&nbsp;+&nbsp;DE</span><span class="lab">License footprint</span></div>
        <div class="tw-rh2-meta-cell"><span class="num">In-house</span><span class="lab">Mgmt + maintenance</span></div>
        <div class="tw-rh2-meta-cell"><span class="num">Broker-led</span><span class="lab">Cody Bishop, principal</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="tw-rh2-card">
        <div class="tw-rh2-card-img">
          <img src="/assets/hero-aerial.jpg" alt="Maryland and Delaware neighborhoods served by Tidewater Realty Group" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
          <span class="tw-rh2-card-badge matched">Free market analysis</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tw-rh2-card-body">
          <div class="tw-rh2-card-price">What&rsquo;s your home worth?</div>
          <div class="tw-rh2-card-addr">A real number from local brokers &mdash; not a Zestimate.</div>
          <div class="tw-rh2-card-stats">
            <span><strong>35+</strong> yrs in market</span>
            <span><strong>MD + DE</strong> licensed</span>
            <span><strong>$0</strong> no-obligation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tw-rh2-card-pitch">
            <div class="tw-rh2-card-pitch-eye">Broker-prepared CMA</div>
            Request a market analysis and we&rsquo;ll hand you a valuation grounded in real comps &mdash; prepared by the broker, not an algorithm.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
